\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Ball detection at release. Green circle~= contour method (preferred); yellow~= Hough fallback. Ball correctly localised at $(938, 680)$, radius $r=46$\,px. Top 15\,\% of frame excluded.}}{10}{figure.caption.21}%
\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Lane calibration: 6 Hough lines (yellow/orange) restricted to the right 55\,\% of the frame, converging to the vanishing point (red circle) at $(1012, 106)$. The player is excluded by the ROI mask (vertical blue line).}}{11}{figure.caption.23}%
\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces 2D ball trajectory over 6.36\,s. Colour encodes time: blue (release) $\to $ yellow (mid) $\to $ red (end). White dots~= raw detections. Arrows indicate direction of travel. The hook of $+168$\,px is annotated with a yellow brace.}}{12}{figure.caption.26}%
\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4}{\ignorespaces Lucas--Kanade tracking on the ball surface crop (5$\times $ magnified inset). Coloured arcs trace the trajectory of 17 feature points across 25 frames. The yellow circle marks the detected finger hole.}}{13}{figure.caption.27}%
